ruriruri
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:? love poems or songs; song, ditty, generally of an amorous nature, accompanied by gestures (Williams p. 352) which Best may  be using light-heartedly; or ? a mis-reading of pukapukas `books'.


